+**Constraints & indexes**
+
+```cypher
+CREATE CONSTRAINT prov_id IF NOT EXISTS FOR (p:Provenance) REQUIRE p.id IS UNIQUE;
+CREATE CONSTRAINT model_key IF NOT EXISTS FOR (m:Model) REQUIRE (m.provider, m.name) IS NODE KEY;
